Siemens is a trusted partner for municipal governments and offers solutions across all infrastructure domains to make cities more efficient, sustainable, and resilient – for instance, with intelligent transportation solutions, efficient and safe buildings, and smart-city initiatives that leverage the power of digitalization.

Goal 12 – Ensure sustainable consumption and production patterns